verbose_text: Total serum phosphorus levels were analyzed with the Ecoline S Phosphate kit (Diasys, Holzheim, Germany) and serum calcium levels were determined with flame atomic absorption spectrometry (FAAS) (Perkin-Elmer Model AAnalyst 800, Wellesley, MA, USA) after appropriate dilution in 0.1% La (NO 3) 3 to eliminate chemical interference.
